SERVER SPAWNS ENTITY (server -> client) ID=0x01



----------------------
ID 0x01 -> server spawns entity
ID 0x0a + (transaction id) -> command suggestion request
ID 0x1a -> client is on ground or not
ID 0x22 + (player id) -> player performed action (crouching, sprinting)
ID 0x12 -> player used F3 + I while looking at entity
ID 0x18 -> set plater position and rotation (player moving)
ID 0x24 -> Pong packer
